Hi everyone!

I'm Nikha, i am from Sikkim. since my work is based out of Jaipur, Rajasthan, i keep juggling from this place to the other. Like many of you i love to travel and meet new people, i think it makes me more wiser and compassionate towards others. I had been very keen on doing something with my space in siliguri and Airbnb is the best decision i made to list my place. i am looking forward to hosting new guests from all over the world for a cultural exchange. " welcomes you with warmth along with an amazing plethora of services and comfortable stays "

Out on a trip? Well, a good hotel or an affordable lodge, away from home, is a pivotal attribute that shall make your holiday a glorious one. If you are on a trip to the sweetest part of India, our hotel near New Jalpaiguri Station in Siliguri, is right at your humble service 24*7.
